name: TROG
description: Welcome to the wacky, wild world of Trog (Trump Frog) - the meme coin that’s here to make crypto great again Combining the meme-worthy charm of a frog with the unmistakable flair of Trump. It’s the crossover you never knew you needed! Just like any great meme, Trog thrives on the support and creativity of its community. Your voice shapes our journey
